HEADWORD: lemmatize
<hw>lem"ma*tize</hw> <pr>(l⟦ecr⟧m"m⟦adot⟧*t⟦imac⟧z`)</pr>, <pos>v.
t.</pos> <def>To convert into a lemma{2}; to normalize the form of (a
