index; <as>as, ⟦ldquo⟧ride⟦rdquo⟧ is the <ex>lemmatized</ex> form for
⟦ldquo⟧riding⟦rdquo⟧ and ⟦ldquo⟧ridden⟦rdquo⟧</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
